reverse polish notation ::

if its a number, push it into the stack, if its an operand, operate on the stack and push the result. now that's a stack if ive ever seen one, so any stackable container will do : hence, stack, apparently

tests : 
	empty stack
	one number stack
	one operand stack
	bad number to operand ratio
	bad input :
		77
		8*
		aaa
		-g
		-9
	random calculations for result checks
